   Run the program and modify it so that it will draw the number of dashes the user specifies
   ~~~~
   import turtle
   line_length = int(input("line length"))
   number_dashes = int(input("number dashes"))
   for n in range(0,2):
       turtle.pendown()
       turtle.forward(line_length)
       turtle.penup()
       turtle.forward(5)